text: trust me folks tax time never gets easier - just more coffee involved! 😅
trust me you're not alone but playing too loose with cash could backfire - seen enough oops moments in my time!
“ever consider surprise healthcare expenses? total budget killers!”
more money doesn’t auto mean better spendings
even after retiring those nurse reflexes check expiration dates constantly
even saw funds once reserved for antique doorknob collection... absurd!
nursing had its stereotypes too - pushed through
mostly locals blab too much nowdays, ain’t nothing stay hidden
word spreads quick in small towns
definitely felt that french touch stick with me
past vibes fade as life goes on
kite battles were art & tradition rolled into one!
